The following plans are included in this Generic HACCP Plan: 1. Surimi. 2. Imitation Crabmeat. 3. Fish, whole, H&G, G&G (parasites). 4. Fish Fillets (Parasites) 5. Squid. 6. Mussels. 7. Crab, Dungeness. 8. Shrimp, Dried. 9. Oysters, Florida. 10. Oysters, raw. Each plan has a product description, flow diagram, potential hazards, and a hazard analysis worksheet.
